    "section_custom_liquid_6xyzG4": {
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{%- comment -%}\nByMetz SEO Intro Block (zonder FAQ)\n- Links zijn locale-aware (blijven in /it, /de, /en, /fr, /es)\n- Niet-NL copy: minder lokaal Eindhoven, meer NL + EU shipping\n- Route knop alleen zichtbaar in NL\n{%- endcomment -%}\n\n{%- assign origin = request.origin | default: shop.url -%}\n{%- assign root = routes.root_url -%}\n{%- if root == '/' -%}{%- assign root = '' -%}{%- endif -%}\n\n{%- assign sort_qs = '?sort_by=created-descending' -%}\n\n{%- comment -%}\nLocale-aware collectie URLs:\nAls je vertaalde handles gebruikt (zoals IT: borse/valigie), dan geeft collections['tassen'].url automatisch /it/collections/borse terug.\n{%- endcomment -%}\n{%- assign url_all_sorted   = origin | append: root | append: '/collections/all' | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_tassen       = collections['tassen'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_koffers      = collections['koffers'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_reistassen   = collections['reistassen'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_rugzakken    = collections['rugzakken'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_schooltassen = collections['schooltassen'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n{%- assign url_laptoptassen = collections['laptoptassen'].url | append: sort_qs -%}\n\n{%- comment -%}\nGoogle Maps route (alleen NL zichtbaar als knop)\n{%- endcomment -%}\n{%- assign maps_directions_url = 'https://www.google.com/maps/dir/?api=1&destination=ByMetz.nl%20-%20Tassen%20%26%20Koffers%2C%20Winkelcentrum%20Woensel%2059%2C%205625%20AD%20Eindhoven&travelmode=driving' -%}\n\n{%- comment -%} Fix voor SearchAction {%- endcomment -%}\n{%- assign search_target = origin | append: root | append: '/search?q=' | append: '{search_term_string}' -%}\n{%- assign store_name = shop.name | default: 'ByMetz' -%}\n\n{%- assign lang = localization.language.iso_code | default: 'nl' -%}\n{%- assign show_route_btn = false -%}\n\n{%- case lang -%}\n\n  {%- when 'nl' -%}\n    {%- assign show_route_btn = true -%}\n\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Tassen kopen in Eindhoven? Ontdek <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span> in Winkelcentrum Woensel{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> is dé <strong>tassenwinkel in Eindhoven</strong> voor <strong>tassen</strong>, <strong>koffers</strong> en <strong>reistassen</strong>. Al meer dan <strong>50 jaar</strong> helpen we je met <strong>persoonlijk advies</strong> en een assortiment voor werk, school en reizen.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Snelle links naar categorieën' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Handtassen & schoudertassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Koffers' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Reistassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Rugzakken' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Schooltassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Laptoptassen' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Shoppen in Eindhoven (Woensel)' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Kom je liever in het echt vergelijken? In onze winkel in <strong>Winkelcentrum Woensel</strong> kun je rustig passen, voelen en kiezen. Of je nu een <strong>handtas</strong>, <strong>koffer</strong>, <strong>reistas</strong>, <strong>rugzak</strong>, <strong>schooltas</strong> of <strong>laptoptas</strong> zoekt: je krijgt eerlijk advies en je ziet direct wat het beste bij je past.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Je shopt bij ons overzichtelijk en comfortabel — met veel keuze, snelle vergelijking en hulp als je twijfelt.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Voor werk, school en reizen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Handtassen</strong> & <strong>schoudertassen</strong> voor elke stijl{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Koffers</strong>: van handbagage tot grote reiskoffers{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Reistassen</strong> voor weekendjes weg en vakantie{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Rugzakken</strong> & <strong>schooltassen</strong> voor dagelijks gebruik{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Laptoptassen</strong> & werktassen voor bescherming en comfort{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = '24/7 online bestellen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Liever direct shoppen? Online kun je snel en eenvoudig <strong>tassen, koffers en reistassen bestellen</strong>. Bekijk het assortiment en ontdek wat er net binnen is gekomen.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Waarom ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Je krijgt service zoals je die van een echt <strong>familiebedrijf</strong> mag verwachten. We helpen je met maat, indeling, materiaal en gebruik — zodat je met een keuze naar huis gaat waar je lang plezier van hebt.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Bekijk het assortiment' -%}\n    {%- assign t_btn_route = 'Route naar de winkel (Google Maps)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Tassenwinkel in Nederland met tassen, koffers en reistassen. Familiebedrijf met persoonlijk advies en online bestellen.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'en' -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Bags & suitcases from the Netherlands — discover <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span>{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> is a Dutch <strong>family-run store</strong> for <strong>bags</strong>, <strong>suitcases</strong> and <strong>travel bags</strong>. We ship <strong>throughout the EU</strong> and have been helping customers for over <strong>50 years</strong> with personal advice and reliable quality.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Quick links to categories' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Handbags & shoulder bags' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Suitcases' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Travel bags' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Backpacks' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'School bags' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Laptop bags' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'A Dutch store, EU-wide delivery' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Looking for a new bag or suitcase? Shop online with confidence: clear product info, secure checkout and fast shipping to <strong>all EU countries</strong>. Need help choosing the right size, layout or material? We’re happy to help.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'From everyday essentials to travel favourites — discover what’s new and choose what fits your style and trip.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'For work, school and travel' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Handbags</strong> & <strong>shoulder bags</strong> for every style{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Suitcases</strong>: carry-on to large sizes{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Travel bags</strong> for weekends and holidays{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Backpacks</strong> & <strong>school bags</strong> for everyday use{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Laptop bags</strong> & work bags for protection and comfort{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = 'Shop online anytime' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Browse the collection and see what just arrived. We deliver across the EU and make it easy to compare options and find the right match.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Why ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}You get the service you expect from a true <strong>family business</strong>. We help you choose with confidence — so you’ll enjoy your purchase for years.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'View the collection' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Dutch bag store shipping across the EU — bags, suitcases and travel bags from a family business.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'de' -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Taschen & Koffer aus den Niederlanden — entdecke <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span>{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> ist ein niederländisches <strong>Familienunternehmen</strong> für <strong>Taschen</strong>, <strong>Koffer</strong> und <strong>Reisetaschen</strong>. Wir liefern <strong>EU-weit</strong> und beraten seit über <strong>50 Jahren</strong> persönlich — online genauso wie im Geschäft.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Schnelllinks zu Kategorien' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Handtaschen & Schultertaschen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Koffer' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Reisetaschen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Rucksäcke' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Schultaschen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Laptoptaschen' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Niederländischer Shop, Lieferung in die EU' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Du suchst die passende Tasche oder den richtigen Koffer? Online findest du klare Infos, sicheren Checkout und Versand in <strong>alle EU-Länder</strong>. Bei Fragen zu Größe, Aufteilung oder Material helfen wir gerne weiter.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Entdecke Neuheiten und vergleiche schnell — so findest du genau das, was zu dir passt.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Für Arbeit, Schule und Reisen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Handtaschen</strong> & <strong>Schultertaschen</strong> für jeden Stil{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Koffer</strong>: Handgepäck bis große Größen{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Reisetaschen</strong> für Wochenenden und Urlaub{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Rucksäcke</strong> & <strong>Schultaschen</strong> für den Alltag{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Laptoptaschen</strong> & Businesstaschen für Schutz und Komfort{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = 'Jederzeit online bestellen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Schau dir das Sortiment an und entdecke, was neu eingetroffen ist. EU-weiter Versand macht den Einkauf einfach — auch über Grenzen hinweg.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Warum ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Service wie im echten <strong>Familienbetrieb</strong>: wir unterstützen dich bei der Wahl, damit du lange Freude daran hast.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Sortiment ansehen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Niederländischer Taschenshop mit EU-weiter Lieferung — Taschen, Koffer und Reisetaschen aus dem Familienbetrieb.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'fr' -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Sacs & valises des Pays-Bas — découvrez <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span>{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> est une <strong>entreprise familiale néerlandaise</strong> spécialisée dans les <strong>sacs</strong>, <strong>valises</strong> et <strong>sacs de voyage</strong>. Nous livrons <strong>dans toute l’UE</strong> et vous conseillons depuis plus de <strong>50 ans</strong>.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Liens rapides vers les catégories' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Sacs à main & bandoulière' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Valises' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Sacs de voyage' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Sacs à dos' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Sacs d’école' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Sacs pour ordinateur' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Boutique néerlandaise, livraison dans l’UE' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Besoin d’un nouveau sac ou d’une valise ? Achetez en ligne en toute confiance : informations claires, paiement sécurisé et livraison <strong>dans tous les pays de l’UE</strong>. Nous vous aidons à choisir la taille, l’organisation et les matériaux.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Découvrez les nouveautés et comparez facilement pour trouver le bon modèle.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Pour le travail, l’école et les voyages' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Sacs à main</strong> & <strong>bandoulière</strong> pour tous les styles{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Valises</strong> : cabine à grand format{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Sacs de voyage</strong> pour week-ends et vacances{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Sacs à dos</strong> & <strong>sacs d’école</strong> pour le quotidien{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Sacs pour ordinateur</strong> & sacs de travail pour confort et protection{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = 'Commander en ligne à tout moment' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Parcourez la sélection et découvrez les nouveautés. La livraison dans l’UE rend l’achat simple, même à l’international.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Pourquoi ByMetz ?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Un service digne d’une vraie <strong>entreprise familiale</strong> : nous vous aidons à choisir, pour un achat durable.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Voir la sélection' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Boutique néerlandaise de sacs avec livraison dans l’UE — sacs, valises et sacs de voyage (entreprise familiale).' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'es' -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Bolsos y maletas desde los Países Bajos — descubre <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span>{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> es una <strong>empresa familiar neerlandesa</strong> de <strong>bolsos</strong>, <strong>maletas</strong> y <strong>bolsas de viaje</strong>. Enviamos a <strong>toda la UE</strong> y llevamos más de <strong>50 años</strong> ayudando con asesoramiento personal.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Enlaces rápidos a categorías' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Bolsos & bandoleras' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Maletas' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Bolsas de viaje' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Mochilas' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Mochilas escolares' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Bolsas para portátil' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Tienda neerlandesa, envíos por la UE' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}¿Buscas un bolso o una maleta nueva? Compra online con tranquilidad: información clara, pago seguro y envíos a <strong>todos los países de la UE</strong>. Te ayudamos a elegir tamaño, distribución y material.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Descubre novedades y compara rápido para encontrar la opción ideal.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Para trabajo, escuela y viajes' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Bolsos</strong> & <strong>bandoleras</strong> para cada estilo{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Maletas</strong>: desde cabina hasta grandes{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Bolsas de viaje</strong> para escapadas y vacaciones{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Mochilas</strong> & <strong>mochilas escolares</strong> para el día a día{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Bolsas para portátil</strong> & bolsas de trabajo para protección y comodidad{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = 'Compra online cuando quieras' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Explora el catálogo y descubre lo nuevo. Con envíos por la UE, comprar desde el extranjero es fácil.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = '¿Por qué ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Servicio de una auténtica <strong>empresa familiar</strong>: te ayudamos a elegir para que disfrutes tu compra durante mucho tiempo.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Ver el catálogo' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Tienda neerlandesa de bolsos con envíos por la UE — bolsos, maletas y bolsas de viaje (empresa familiar).' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'it' -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Borse e valigie dai Paesi Bassi — scopri <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span>{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> è un’<strong>azienda di famiglia olandese</strong> specializzata in <strong>borse</strong>, <strong>valigie</strong> e <strong>borse da viaggio</strong>. Spediamo in <strong>tutta l’UE</strong> e da oltre <strong>50 anni</strong> aiutiamo i clienti con consigli personalizzati.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Link rapidi alle categorie' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Borse & borse a tracolla' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Valigie' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Borse da viaggio' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Zaini' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Zaini scuola' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Borse per laptop' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Negozio olandese, spedizione in UE' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Cerchi una borsa o una valigia nuova? Acquista online in modo sicuro: informazioni chiare, pagamento protetto e spedizione in <strong>tutti i paesi dell’UE</strong>. Ti aiutiamo a scegliere dimensioni, organizzazione e materiali.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Scopri le novità e confronta facilmente per trovare la scelta giusta.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Per lavoro, scuola e viaggi' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Borse</strong> & <strong>borse a tracolla</strong> per ogni stile{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Valigie</strong>: dal bagaglio a mano alle grandi{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Borse da viaggio</strong> per weekend e vacanze{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Zaini</strong> & <strong>zaini scuola</strong> per l’uso quotidiano{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Borse per laptop</strong> & borse da lavoro per protezione e comfort{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = 'Ordina online quando vuoi' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Sfoglia l’assortimento e scopri le ultime novità. Con spedizione in UE, acquistare dall’estero è semplice.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Perché ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Servizio da vera <strong>azienda di famiglia</strong>: ti aiutiamo a scegliere con sicurezza, per un acquisto che dura.{%- endcapture -%}\n\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Scopri l’assortimento' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Negozio olandese di borse con spedizione in UE — borse, valigie e borse da viaggio (azienda di famiglia).' -%}\n\n  {%- else -%}\n    {%- comment -%}Fallback → gebruik NL copy zonder zichtbare debug-tekst{%- endcomment -%}\n    {%- assign show_route_btn = true -%}\n    {%- capture t_title -%}Tassen kopen in Eindhoven? Ontdek <span class=\"bm-logo-text\">ByMetz</span> in Winkelcentrum Woensel{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_lead -%}<strong>ByMetz</strong> is dé <strong>tassenwinkel in Eindhoven</strong> voor <strong>tassen</strong>, <strong>koffers</strong> en <strong>reistassen</strong>. Al meer dan <strong>50 jaar</strong> helpen we je met <strong>persoonlijk advies</strong> en een assortiment voor werk, school en reizen.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_quicklinks_aria = 'Snelle links naar categorieën' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_tassen = 'Handtassen & schoudertassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_koffers = 'Koffers' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_reistassen = 'Reistassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_rugzakken = 'Rugzakken' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_schooltassen = 'Schooltassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_chip_laptoptassen = 'Laptoptassen' -%}\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_1 = 'Shoppen in Eindhoven (Woensel)' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_left_1 -%}Kom je liever in het echt vergelijken? In onze winkel in <strong>Winkelcentrum Woensel</strong> kun je rustig passen, voelen en kiezen.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_p_left_2 = 'Je shopt bij ons overzichtelijk en comfortabel — met veel keuze, snelle vergelijking en hulp als je twijfelt.' -%}\n    {%- assign t_h3_left_2 = 'Voor werk, school en reizen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_1 -%}<strong>Handtassen</strong> & <strong>schoudertassen</strong> voor elke stijl{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_2 -%}<strong>Koffers</strong>: van handbagage tot grote reiskoffers{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_3 -%}<strong>Reistassen</strong> voor weekendjes weg en vakantie{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_4 -%}<strong>Rugzakken</strong> & <strong>schooltassen</strong> voor dagelijks gebruik{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- capture t_li_5 -%}<strong>Laptoptassen</strong> & werktassen voor bescherming en comfort{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_1 = '24/7 online bestellen' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_1 -%}Liever direct shoppen? Online kun je snel en eenvoudig <strong>tassen, koffers en reistassen bestellen</strong>.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_h3_right_2 = 'Waarom ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture t_p_right_2 -%}Je krijgt service zoals je die van een echt <strong>familiebedrijf</strong> mag verwachten.{%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign t_btn_primary = 'Bekijk het assortiment' -%}\n    {%- assign t_btn_route = 'Route naar de winkel (Google Maps)' -%}\n    {%- assign t_store_description = 'Tassenwinkel in Nederland met tassen, koffers en reistassen. Familiebedrijf met persoonlijk advies en online bestellen.' -%}\n{%- endcase -%}\n\n{%- comment -%} Schema taal dynamisch {%- endcomment -%}\n{%- capture schema_lang -%}{{ localization.language.iso_code | default: 'nl' }}-{{ localization.country.iso_code | default: 'NL' }}{%- endcapture -%}\n\n<section class=\"bymetz-seo\" aria-labelledby=\"bymetz-seo-title\">\n  <header class=\"bymetz-seo__header\">\n    <h2 id=\"bymetz-seo-title\" class=\"bymetz-seo__title\">{{ t_title }}</h2>\n    <p class=\"bymetz-seo__lead\">{{ t_lead }}</p>\n  </header>\n\n  <nav class=\"bymetz-seo__quicklinks\" aria-label=\"{{ t_quicklinks_aria }}\">\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_tassen }}\">{{ t_chip_tassen }}</a>\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_koffers }}\">{{ t_chip_koffers }}</a>\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_reistassen }}\">{{ t_chip_reistassen }}</a>\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_rugzakken }}\">{{ t_chip_rugzakken }}</a>\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_schooltassen }}\">{{ t_chip_schooltassen }}</a>\n    <a class=\"bymetz-seo__chip\" href=\"{{ url_laptoptassen }}\">{{ t_chip_laptoptassen }}</a>\n  </nav>\n\n  <div class=\"bymetz-seo__grid\">\n    <div class=\"bymetz-seo__col\">\n      <h3 class=\"bymetz-seo__h3\">{{ t_h3_left_1 }}</h3>\n      <p class=\"bymetz-seo__text\">{{ t_p_left_1 }}</p>\n      <p class=\"bymetz-seo__text\">{{ t_p_left_2 }}</p>\n\n      <h3 class=\"bymetz-seo__h3\">{{ t_h3_left_2 }}</h3>\n      <ul class=\"bymetz-seo__list\">\n        <li>{{ t_li_1 }}</li>\n        <li>{{ t_li_2 }}</li>\n        <li>{{ t_li_3 }}</li>\n        <li>{{ t_li_4 }}</li>\n        <li>{{ t_li_5 }}</li>\n      </ul>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"bymetz-seo__col\">\n      <h3 class=\"bymetz-seo__h3\">{{ t_h3_right_1 }}</h3>\n      <p class=\"bymetz-seo__text\">{{ t_p_right_1 }}</p>\n\n      <h3 class=\"bymetz-seo__h3\">{{ t_h3_right_2 }}</h3>\n      <p class=\"bymetz-seo__text\">{{ t_p_right_2 }}</p>\n\n      <div class=\"bymetz-seo__cta\">\n        <a class=\"bymetz-seo__btn bymetz-seo__btn--primary\" href=\"{{ url_all_sorted }}\">\n          {{ t_btn_primary }}\n        </a>\n\n        {%- if show_route_btn -%}\n          <a class=\"bymetz-seo__btn bymetz-seo__btn--ghost\" href=\"{{ maps_directions_url | escape }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">\n            {{ t_btn_route }}\n          </a>\n        {%- endif -%}\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .bymetz-seo{ max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:56px 20px; }\n\n  .bymetz-seo__title{\n    text-align:center;\n    font-weight:800;\n    line-height:1.15;\n    margin:0 0 18px;\n    font-size:clamp(26px,3.4vw,44px);\n    letter-spacing:-0.025em;\n    color:#1a1a1a;\n  }\n\n  /* Refined highlight on ByMetz: gradient underline (no chunky bg) */\n  .bymetz-seo__hl{\n    position:relative;\n    display:inline-block;\n    font-weight:800;\n    color:#E65324;\n    padding:0 .04em;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__hl::after{\n    content:\"\";\n    position:absolute;\n    left:0; right:0;\n    bottom:.04em;\n    height:3px;\n    background:linear-gradient(90deg,#E65324 0%,#F58800 100%);\n    border-radius:2px;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__hl::before{ display:none; }\n\n  .bymetz-seo__lead{\n    text-align:center;\n    margin:0 auto 32px;\n    max-width:760px;\n    line-height:1.7;\n    font-size:16px;\n    color:#555;\n    font-weight:400;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__lead strong{ color:#1a1a1a; font-weight:600; }\n\n  /* Category chips: subtle, clean */\n  .bymetz-seo__quicklinks{\n    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:8px;\n    justify-content:center;\n    margin:0 0 48px;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__chip{\n    display:inline-flex; align-items:center;\n    padding:9px 16px;\n    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.12);\n    border-radius:999px;\n    background:#fff;\n    color:#444;\n    text-decoration:none;\n    font-size:13px;\n    font-weight:500;\n    line-height:1;\n    white-space:nowrap;\n    transition:border-color .25s ease,color .25s ease,background-color .25s ease,transform .25s ease,box-shadow .25s ease;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__chip:hover,\n  .bymetz-seo__chip:focus{\n    border-color:#E65324;\n    color:#E65324;\n    background:#FFF8F5;\n    transform:translateY(-1px);\n    box-shadow:0 4px 12px rgba(230,83,36,.12);\n  }\n\n  /* Two-column grid */\n  .bymetz-seo__grid{\n    display:grid; gap:48px;\n    grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;\n    align-items:start;\n  }\n\n  .bymetz-seo__h3{\n    margin:0 0 12px;\n    font-weight:700;\n    line-height:1.3;\n    font-size:17px;\n    color:#1a1a1a;\n    letter-spacing:-0.01em;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__text + .bymetz-seo__h3,\n  .bymetz-seo__list + .bymetz-seo__h3{ margin-top:28px; }\n\n  .bymetz-seo__text{\n    margin:0 0 14px;\n    line-height:1.75;\n    font-size:15px;\n    color:#555;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__text strong{ color:#1a1a1a; font-weight:600; }\n\n  .bymetz-seo__list{\n    margin:0;\n    padding-left:18px;\n    line-height:1.9;\n    font-size:15px;\n    color:#555;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__list strong{ color:#1a1a1a; font-weight:600; }\n\n  /* CTA buttons */\n  .bymetz-seo__cta{\n    display:flex; flex-wrap:wrap; gap:12px;\n    margin-top:28px;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__btn{\n    display:inline-flex; align-items:center;\n    gap:8px;\n    padding:14px 24px;\n    border-radius:6px;\n    text-decoration:none !important;\n    font-weight:600;\n    font-size:14px;\n    letter-spacing:0.02em;\n    line-height:1.2;\n    border:1px solid transparent;\n    transition:background-color .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1),border-color .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1),color .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1),transform .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1),box-shadow .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);\n  }\n\n  /* Primary: solid brand orange with arrow + hover lift */\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:visited{\n    background:#E65324;\n    border-color:#E65324;\n    color:#fff !important;\n    box-shadow:0 4px 14px rgba(230,83,36,.25);\n    opacity:1 !important;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary::after{\n    content:\"\\2192\";\n    display:inline-block;\n    font-size:16px;\n    font-weight:400;\n    transition:transform .3s cubic-bezier(.2,.7,.3,1);\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:hover,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:focus,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:active{\n    background:#d4441a;\n    border-color:#d4441a;\n    color:#fff !important;\n    transform:translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow:0 8px 24px rgba(230,83,36,.35);\n    opacity:1 !important;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:hover::after,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--primary:focus::after{ transform:translateX(4px); }\n\n  /* Ghost: clean outline with subtle hover */\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--ghost,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--ghost:visited{\n    background:#fff;\n    border-color:rgba(0,0,0,.15);\n    color:#1a1a1a !important;\n  }\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--ghost:hover,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--ghost:focus,\n  .bymetz-seo__btn--ghost:active{\n    background:#fff;\n    border-color:#1a1a1a;\n    color:#1a1a1a !important;\n    transform:translateY(-2px);\n    box-shadow:0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,.08);\n    opacity:1 !important;\n  }\n\n  @media (max-width: 900px){\n    .bymetz-seo{ padding:40px 16px; }\n    .bymetz-seo__grid{ grid-template-columns:1fr; gap:32px; }\n    .bymetz-seo__lead{ font-size:15px; margin-bottom:24px; }\n    .bymetz-seo__quicklinks{ gap:6px; margin-bottom:32px; }\n    .bymetz-seo__chip{ padding:8px 13px; font-size:12px; }\n    .bymetz-seo__btn{ width:100%; justify-content:center; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\": \"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@graph\": [\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"WebSite\",\n      \"@id\": {{ origin | append: root | append: \"#website\" | json }},\n      \"url\": {{ origin | append: root | json }},\n      \"name\": {{ store_name | json }},\n      \"inLanguage\": {{ schema_lang | json }},\n      \"potentialAction\": {\n        \"@type\": \"SearchAction\",\n        \"target\": {{ search_target | json }},\n        \"query-input\": \"required name=search_term_string\"\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\": \"Store\",\n      \"@id\": {{ origin | append: root | append: \"#store\" | json }},\n      \"name\": {{ store_name | json }},\n      \"url\": {{ origin | append: root | json }},\n      \"inLanguage\": {{ schema_lang | json }},\n      \"areaServed\": \"EU\",\n      \"description\": {{ t_store_description | json }},\n      \"telephone\": {{ shop.phone | default: \"\" | json }},\n      \"email\": {{ shop.email | default: \"\" | json }},\n      \"address\": {\n        \"@type\": \"PostalAddress\",\n        \"streetAddress\": \"Winkelcentrum Woensel 59\",\n        \"postalCode\": \"5625 AD\",\n        \"addressLocality\": \"Eindhoven\",\n        \"addressRegion\": \"Noord-Brabant\",\n        \"addressCountry\": \"NL\"\n      }\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</script>"
