    "section_custom_liquid_mbnTzn": {
      "settings": {
        "custom_liquid": "{%- comment -%}\nByMetz FAQ Block (los te plaatsen)\n- NL: exact originele teksten/FAQ (ongewijzigd)\n- EN: parkeren blijft + aangepaste shipping zin\n- DE/FR/ES/IT: geen parkeren; wel snelle & verzekerde verzending naar het land van de taal\n- Inclusief JSON-LD FAQPage per taal\n{%- endcomment -%}\n\n{%- assign base_url = shop.url | default: request.origin -%}\n{%- assign whatsapp_url = 'https://wa.me/message/NHENYUN3AYQMN1' -%}\n{%- assign lang = localization.language.iso_code | default: 'nl' -%}\n\n{%- case lang -%}\n\n  {%- when 'en' -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Frequently asked questions (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = 'Where is ByMetz located?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Our physical store is in the <strong>Netherlands</strong>. Address: <strong>Winkelcentrum Woensel 59</strong>, <strong>5625 AD</strong>, <strong>Eindhoven</strong>.\n        Shopping from abroad? You can order online — we ship <strong>throughout the EU</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'Our physical store is in the Netherlands. Address: Winkelcentrum Woensel 59, 5625 AD, Eindhoven. You can also order online with EU-wide shipping.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = 'Is parking available when visiting the store?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Yes. You can park <strong>directly behind the store</strong> and the back exit takes you straight to your car.\n        At <strong>Woensel Shopping Center</strong> there are plenty of parking spaces and parking costs <strong>€0.60 per hour</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Yes. You can park directly behind the store and reach your car easily via the back exit. Woensel Shopping Center has plenty of parking spaces and parking costs €0.60 per hour.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = 'Can I order bags and suitcases online?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Yes. You can shop online 24/7 and order your favourite <strong>bag</strong>, <strong>suitcase</strong> or <strong>travel bag</strong>.\n        <strong>Reduced or free shipping within the EU on higher order values.</strong>\n        We have received <strong>1700+ reviews</strong> with an average rating of <strong>9.6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Yes. Shop online 24/7 and order bags, suitcases and travel bags. Reduced or free shipping within the EU on higher order values. We have 1700+ reviews with an average rating of 9.6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = 'Which products does ByMetz sell?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz sells <strong>handbags</strong>, <strong>shoulder bags</strong>, <strong>backpacks</strong>, <strong>school bags</strong>,\n        <strong>laptop bags</strong>, <strong>suitcases</strong>, <strong>travel bags</strong>, plus <strong>wallets</strong>, <strong>belts</strong> and <strong>jewellery</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz sells handbags, shoulder bags, backpacks, school bags, laptop bags, suitcases, travel bags, wallets, belts and jewellery.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = 'Can you help me choose the right bag or suitcase?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Yes. We’re happy to help with personal advice on size, weight, layout, material and use (work, school or travel).\n        You can get advice in-store and easily via WhatsApp:\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">send us a message on WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Yes. We provide personal advice on size, weight, layout, material and use. You can get advice in-store and via WhatsApp.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = 'Is ByMetz the largest bag and suitcase store in the Netherlands?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Yes. ByMetz has <strong>2 floors</strong> and more than <strong>500 m²</strong> of retail space.\n        This makes it easy to compare many models, sizes and styles — from everyday bags to travel and business options.\n        Our suitcase department is exceptionally spacious, helping you quickly find the right suitcase based on <strong>size</strong>, <strong>weight</strong>,\n        <strong>layout</strong> and your type of trip.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Yes. ByMetz has 2 floors and over 500 m² of retail space, making it easy to compare many models, sizes and styles. The suitcase department is exceptionally spacious, helping you find the right suitcase based on size, weight, layout and your trip type.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'de' -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Häufige Fragen (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = 'Wo befindet sich ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Unser Ladengeschäft befindet sich in den <strong>Niederlanden</strong> (Eindhoven).\n        Du kannst aber auch bequem online bestellen — wir liefern nach <strong>Deutschland</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'Unser Ladengeschäft befindet sich in den Niederlanden (Eindhoven). Online bestellen ist möglich; wir liefern nach Deutschland.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = 'Wie schnell wird nach Deutschland geliefert?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Wir versenden <strong>schnell und versichert nach Deutschland</strong>. Du erhältst eine Sendungsverfolgung (Track &amp; Trace)\n        und wir verpacken sorgfältig, damit deine Tasche oder dein Koffer sicher ankommt.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Wir versenden schnell und versichert nach Deutschland, inklusive Sendungsverfolgung und sorgfältiger Verpackung.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = 'Kann ich Taschen und Koffer online bestellen?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. Du kannst 24/7 online shoppen und deine <strong>Tasche</strong>, deinen <strong>Koffer</strong> oder deine <strong>Reisetasche</strong> bestellen.\n        <strong>Gratis Versand ab 49 € nach Deutschland!</strong>\n        Außerdem haben wir <strong>1700+ Bewertungen</strong> mit einem Durchschnitt von <strong>9,6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Ja. 24/7 online shoppen und Taschen, Koffer und Reisetaschen bestellen. Gratis Versand ab 49 € nach Deutschland! 1700+ Bewertungen mit einem Durchschnitt von 9,6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = 'Welche Produkte verkauft ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz verkauft u. a. <strong>Handtaschen</strong>, <strong>Schultertaschen</strong>, <strong>Rucksäcke</strong>, <strong>Schultaschen</strong>,\n        <strong>Laptoptaschen</strong>, <strong>Koffer</strong>, <strong>Reisetaschen</strong> sowie <strong>Geldbörsen</strong>, <strong>Gürtel</strong> und <strong>Schmuck</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz verkauft u. a. Handtaschen, Schultertaschen, Rucksäcke, Schultaschen, Laptoptaschen, Koffer, Reisetaschen, Geldbörsen, Gürtel und Schmuck.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = 'Helft ihr bei der Auswahl des richtigen Koffers oder der richtigen Tasche?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. Wir helfen gerne mit persönlicher Beratung zu Größe, Gewicht, Aufteilung, Material und Nutzung.\n        Das geht einfach per WhatsApp:\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">schreib uns eine WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Ja. Wir beraten persönlich zu Größe, Gewicht, Aufteilung, Material und Nutzung. Beratung via WhatsApp ist möglich.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = 'Ist ByMetz der größte Taschen- und Kofferladen der Niederlande?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. ByMetz hat <strong>2 Etagen</strong> und mehr als <strong>500 m²</strong> Verkaufsfläche.\n        Dadurch kannst du viele Modelle, Größen und Stile direkt vergleichen — von Alltagstaschen bis Reise- und Businesslösungen.\n        Für Koffer haben wir eine außergewöhnlich große Abteilung, sodass du schnell den passenden Koffer findest — nach <strong>Größe</strong>, <strong>Gewicht</strong>,\n        <strong>Aufteilung</strong> und Reisetyp.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Ja. ByMetz hat 2 Etagen und über 500 m² Verkaufsfläche, sodass viele Modelle, Größen und Stile vergleichbar sind. Die Kofferabteilung ist besonders groß und hilft bei der Auswahl nach Größe, Gewicht, Aufteilung und Reisetyp.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'fr' -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Questions fréquentes (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = 'Où se trouve ByMetz ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Notre boutique physique se trouve aux <strong>Pays-Bas</strong> (Eindhoven).\n        Vous pouvez aussi commander en ligne — nous livrons en <strong>Belgique</strong> et en <strong>France</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'Notre boutique physique se trouve aux Pays-Bas (Eindhoven). Vous pouvez commander en ligne; livraison en Belgique et en France.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = 'Livrez-vous rapidement et avec assurance en Belgique et en France ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Oui. Nous expédions <strong>rapidement et avec assurance</strong> en <strong>Belgique</strong> et en <strong>France</strong>.\n        Vous recevez un suivi d’envoi et nous emballons soigneusement pour une livraison sécurisée.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Oui. Expédition rapide et assurée en Belgique et en France, avec suivi et emballage soigné.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = 'Puis-je commander des sacs et des valises en ligne ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Oui. Vous pouvez acheter en ligne 24/7 et commander votre <strong>sac</strong>, votre <strong>valise</strong> ou votre <strong>sac de voyage</strong>.\n        <strong>Livraison gratuite en Belgique dès 29 € et en France dès 99 €.</strong>\n        Nous avons reçu <strong>plus de 1700 avis</strong> avec une note moyenne de <strong>9,6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Oui. Achat en ligne 24/7 : sacs, valises et sacs de voyage. Livraison gratuite en Belgique dès 29 € et en France dès 99 €. Plus de 1700 avis avec une note moyenne de 9,6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = 'Quels produits vend ByMetz ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz vend notamment des <strong>sacs à main</strong>, <strong>sacs bandoulière</strong>, <strong>sacs à dos</strong>, <strong>sacs d’école</strong>,\n        <strong>sacs pour ordinateur</strong>, <strong>valises</strong>, <strong>sacs de voyage</strong>, ainsi que des <strong>portefeuilles</strong>, <strong>ceintures</strong> et <strong>bijoux</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz vend notamment des sacs à main, sacs bandoulière, sacs à dos, sacs d’école, sacs pour ordinateur, valises, sacs de voyage, portefeuilles, ceintures et bijoux.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = 'Pouvez-vous aider à choisir la bonne valise ou le bon sac ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Oui. Nous vous conseillons sur la taille, le poids, l’organisation, les matériaux et l’usage.\n        Facile via WhatsApp :\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">nous envoyer un message sur WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Oui. Conseils personnalisés sur la taille, le poids, l’organisation, les matériaux et l’usage. Assistance via WhatsApp.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = 'ByMetz est-il le plus grand magasin de sacs et valises des Pays-Bas ?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Oui. ByMetz dispose de <strong>2 étages</strong> et de plus de <strong>500 m²</strong> de surface de vente.\n        Vous pouvez comparer de nombreux modèles, tailles et styles — des sacs du quotidien aux solutions de voyage et professionnelles.\n        Notre rayon valises est particulièrement vaste, pour choisir rapidement selon la <strong>taille</strong>, le <strong>poids</strong>,\n        l’<strong>organisation</strong> et votre type de voyage.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Oui. ByMetz a 2 étages et plus de 500 m² de surface de vente, ce qui permet de comparer de nombreux modèles, tailles et styles. Le rayon valises est particulièrement vaste pour choisir selon taille, poids, organisation et type de voyage.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'es' -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Preguntas frecuentes (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = '¿Dónde está ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Nuestra tienda física está en los <strong>Países Bajos</strong> (Eindhoven).\n        También puedes comprar online — enviamos a <strong>España</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'Nuestra tienda física está en los Países Bajos (Eindhoven). También puedes comprar online; enviamos a España.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = '¿Enviáis rápido y asegurado a España?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sí. Enviamos <strong>rápido y asegurado a España</strong>, con seguimiento del envío y embalaje cuidadoso para una entrega segura.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Sí. Envío rápido y asegurado a España, con seguimiento y embalaje cuidadoso para una entrega segura.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = '¿Puedo pedir bolsos y maletas online?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sí. Puedes comprar online 24/7 y pedir tu <strong>bolso</strong>, <strong>maleta</strong> o <strong>bolsa de viaje</strong>.\n        <strong>Envío gratuito a España a partir de 79 €.</strong>\n        Hemos recibido <strong>más de 1700 reseñas</strong> con una puntuación media de <strong>9,6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Sí. Compra online 24/7: bolsos, maletas y bolsas de viaje. Envío gratuito a España a partir de 79 €. Más de 1700 reseñas con una media de 9,6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = '¿Qué productos vende ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz vende <strong>bolsos</strong>, <strong>bandoleras</strong>, <strong>mochilas</strong>, <strong>mochilas escolares</strong>,\n        <strong>bolsas para portátil</strong>, <strong>maletas</strong>, <strong>bolsas de viaje</strong>, además de <strong>carteras</strong>, <strong>cinturones</strong> y <strong>joyería</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz vende bolsos, bandoleras, mochilas, mochilas escolares, bolsas para portátil, maletas, bolsas de viaje, carteras, cinturones y joyería.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = '¿Ayudáis a elegir la maleta o el bolso adecuado?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sí. Te ayudamos con asesoramiento personal sobre tamaño, peso, distribución, material y uso.\n        Fácil por WhatsApp:\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">envíanos un mensaje por WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Sí. Asesoramiento personal sobre tamaño, peso, distribución, material y uso. Asistencia por WhatsApp.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = '¿Es ByMetz la tienda de bolsos y maletas más grande de los Países Bajos?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sí. ByMetz tiene <strong>2 plantas</strong> y más de <strong>500 m²</strong> de superficie.\n        Así puedes comparar muchos modelos, tamaños y estilos — desde bolsos de diario hasta opciones de viaje y de negocios.\n        Nuestra sección de maletas es excepcionalmente amplia, para elegir rápido según <strong>tamaño</strong>, <strong>peso</strong>,\n        <strong>distribución</strong> y tipo de viaje.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Sí. ByMetz tiene 2 plantas y más de 500 m², lo que permite comparar muchos modelos, tamaños y estilos. La sección de maletas es muy amplia para elegir según tamaño, peso, distribución y tipo de viaje.' -%}\n\n  {%- when 'it' -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Domande frequenti (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = 'Dove si trova ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Il nostro negozio fisico è nei <strong>Paesi Bassi</strong> (Eindhoven).\n        Puoi anche acquistare online — spediamo in <strong>Italia</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'Il nostro negozio fisico è nei Paesi Bassi (Eindhoven). Puoi acquistare online; spediamo in Italia.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = 'Spedite velocemente e con assicurazione in Italia?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sì. Spediamo <strong>rapidamente e con assicurazione in Italia</strong>, con tracciamento e imballaggio accurato per una consegna sicura.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Sì. Spedizione rapida e assicurata in Italia, con tracciamento e imballaggio accurato per una consegna sicura.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = 'Posso ordinare borse e valigie online?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sì. Puoi fare shopping online 24/7 e ordinare la tua <strong>borsa</strong>, <strong>valigia</strong> o <strong>borsa da viaggio</strong>.\n        <strong>Spedizione gratuita a partire da €99.</strong>\n        Abbiamo ricevuto <strong>oltre 1700 recensioni</strong> con una media di <strong>9,6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Sì. Shopping online 24/7: borse, valigie e borse da viaggio. Spedizione gratuita a partire da €99. Oltre 1700 recensioni con media 9,6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = 'Quali prodotti vende ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz vende <strong>borse</strong>, <strong>borse a tracolla</strong>, <strong>zaini</strong>, <strong>zaini scuola</strong>,\n        <strong>borse per laptop</strong>, <strong>valigie</strong>, <strong>borse da viaggio</strong>, oltre a <strong>portafogli</strong>, <strong>cinture</strong> e <strong>gioielli</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz vende borse, borse a tracolla, zaini, zaini scuola, borse per laptop, valigie, borse da viaggio, portafogli, cinture e gioielli.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = 'Aiutate a scegliere la borsa o la valigia giusta?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sì. Offriamo consigli personalizzati su dimensioni, peso, organizzazione, materiale e utilizzo.\n        Facile via WhatsApp:\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">scrivici su WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Sì. Consulenza personalizzata su dimensioni, peso, organizzazione, materiale e utilizzo. Assistenza via WhatsApp.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = 'ByMetz è il più grande negozio di borse e valigie dei Paesi Bassi?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Sì. ByMetz ha <strong>2 piani</strong> e oltre <strong>500 m²</strong> di superficie.\n        Puoi confrontare molti modelli, dimensioni e stili — dalle borse di tutti i giorni alle soluzioni da viaggio e business.\n        Il reparto valigie è eccezionalmente ampio, così trovi rapidamente quella giusta in base a <strong>dimensioni</strong>, <strong>peso</strong>,\n        <strong>organizzazione</strong> e tipo di viaggio.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Sì. ByMetz ha 2 piani e oltre 500 m², permettendo di confrontare molti modelli, dimensioni e stili. Il reparto valigie è molto ampio per scegliere in base a dimensioni, peso, organizzazione e tipo di viaggio.' -%}\n\n  {%- else -%}\n    {%- comment -%} NL default: exact originele FAQ + teksten (ongewijzigd) {%- endcomment -%}\n    {%- assign faq_title = 'Veelgestelde vragen (FAQ)' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q1 = 'Wat is het adres van ByMetz en hoe kom ik er het snelst?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a1_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz is gevestigd op <strong>Winkelcentrum Woensel 59</strong>, <strong>5625 AD</strong> <strong>Eindhoven</strong>.\n        De snelste route plan je via <strong>Google Maps</strong> door op dit adres te navigeren.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a1_schema = 'ByMetz is gevestigd op Winkelcentrum Woensel 59, 5625 AD Eindhoven. De snelste route plan je via Google Maps door te navigeren op dit adres.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q2 = 'Kan ik makkelijk parkeren bij de winkel van ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a2_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. Je kunt <strong>direct achter de winkel</strong> parkeren en via de <strong>achteruitgang</strong> loop je zó naar je auto.\n        Ideaal, want je hoeft niet het hele winkelcentrum door met je nieuwe koffer.\n        In <strong>Winkelcentrum Woensel</strong> zijn bovendien ontzettend veel parkeerplekken en parkeren kost slechts <strong>€0,60 per uur</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a2_schema = 'Ja. Je kunt direct achter de winkel parkeren en via de achteruitgang loop je zo naar je auto. In Winkelcentrum Woensel zijn veel parkeerplekken en parkeren kost €0,60 per uur.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q3 = 'Kan ik online tassen, koffers en reistassen bestellen?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a3_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. Je kunt 24/7 online shoppen en direct jouw favoriete <strong>tas</strong>, <strong>koffer</strong> of <strong>reistas</strong> bestellen.\n        Bestellingen vanaf <strong>€29</strong> verzenden we <strong>gratis</strong>.\n        En fijn om te weten: we hebben inmiddels <strong>meer dan 1700 beoordelingen</strong> mogen ontvangen met een gemiddelde score van <strong>9,6</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a3_schema = 'Ja. Je kunt 24/7 online shoppen en tassen, koffers en reistassen bestellen. Bestellingen vanaf €29 verzenden we gratis. We hebben meer dan 1700 beoordelingen ontvangen met een gemiddelde score van 9,6.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q4 = 'Welke producten verkoopt ByMetz?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a4_html -%}\n      <p>\n        ByMetz verkoopt onder andere <strong>handtassen</strong>, <strong>schoudertassen</strong>, <strong>rugzakken</strong>, <strong>schooltassen</strong>,\n        <strong>laptoptassen</strong>, <strong>koffers</strong>, <strong>reistassen</strong>, <strong>portemonnees</strong>, <strong>riemen</strong> en <strong>sieraden</strong>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a4_schema = 'ByMetz verkoopt onder andere handtassen, schoudertassen, rugzakken, schooltassen, laptoptassen, koffers, reistassen, portemonnees, riemen en sieraden.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q5 = 'Helpen jullie met het kiezen van de juiste koffer of tas?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a5_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. We helpen je graag met persoonlijk advies over formaat, gewicht, indeling, materiaal en gebruik (werk, school of reis).\n        Dat kan in de winkel én eenvoudig via WhatsApp:\n        <a class=\"bymetz-faq__link\" href=\"{{ whatsapp_url }}\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">stuur ons een bericht via WhatsApp</a>.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a5_schema = 'Ja. We geven persoonlijk advies over formaat, gewicht, indeling, materiaal en gebruik. Dat kan in de winkel én via WhatsApp.' -%}\n\n    {%- assign faq_q6 = 'Is ByMetz de grootste tassen- en kofferwinkel van Nederland?' -%}\n    {%- capture faq_a6_html -%}\n      <p>\n        Ja. ByMetz heeft <strong>2 verdiepingen</strong> en meer dan <strong>500 m²</strong> winkeloppervlak.\n        Daardoor kun je bij ons heel veel modellen, maten en stijlen in één keer vergelijken — van dagelijkse tassen tot reis- en zakenoplossingen.\n        Voor koffers hebben we een uitzonderlijk ruime afdeling, waardoor je snel de juiste koffer vindt op basis van <strong>formaat</strong>, <strong>gewicht</strong>,\n        <strong>indeling</strong> en jouw type reis.\n      </p>\n    {%- endcapture -%}\n    {%- assign faq_a6_schema = 'Ja. ByMetz heeft 2 verdiepingen en meer dan 500 m² winkeloppervlak. Daardoor kun je veel modellen, maten en stijlen vergelijken en snel de juiste tas of koffer vinden op basis van formaat, gewicht, indeling en jouw type reis.' -%}\n\n{%- endcase -%}\n\n<section class=\"bymetz-faq\" aria-labelledby=\"bymetz-faq-title\">\n  <h3 id=\"bymetz-faq-title\" class=\"bymetz-faq__title\">{{ faq_title }}</h3>\n\n  <div class=\"bymetz-faq__items\">\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q1 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a1_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q2 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a2_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q3 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a3_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q4 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a4_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q5 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a5_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n\n    <details class=\"bymetz-faq__item\">\n      <summary>{{ faq_q6 }}</summary>\n      <div class=\"bymetz-faq__answer\">{{ faq_a6_html }}</div>\n    </details>\n  </div>\n</section>\n\n<style>\n  .bymetz-faq{ max-width:1100px; margin:0 auto; padding:26px 16px; }\n  .bymetz-faq__title{ margin:0 0 12px; font-weight:900; font-size:1.25em; line-height:1.2; }\n\n  .bymetz-faq__item{\n    border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,.10);\n    border-radius:12px;\n    padding:10px 12px;\n    margin-top:10px;\n    background:#fff;\n  }\n  .bymetz-faq__item summary{ cursor:pointer; font-weight:900; }\n  .bymetz-faq__answer{ margin-top:8px; line-height:1.7; }\n\n  .bymetz-faq__link{ font-weight:800; text-decoration: underline; }\n</style>\n\n<script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n{\n  \"@context\":\"https://schema.org\",\n  \"@type\":\"FAQPage\",\n  \"@id\": {{ base_url | append: \"#faq\" | json }},\n  \"mainEntity\":[\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q1 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a1_schema | json }}}\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q2 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a2_schema | json }}}\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q3 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a3_schema | json }}}\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q4 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a4_schema | json }}}\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q5 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a5_schema | json }}}\n    },\n    {\n      \"@type\":\"Question\",\n      \"name\": {{ faq_q6 | json }},\n      \"acceptedAnswer\":{\"@type\":\"Answer\",\"text\": {{ faq_a6_schema | json }}}\n    }\n  ]\n}\n</script>"
      },
